  "comment": "The EclFresnel JrVW is a compact LED Fresnel lamp, designed as a replacement for a 600W fixture, with a bright and high-quality variable-white light, from 2,700K to 5,600K, using a 150W LED source. \nThis is the perfect luminaire for those applications requiring high-quality white rendering, such as in TV studios, galleries, and virtual productions, with high CRI (>96), TLCI (>96), TM-30 and R9.\n\nThe EclFresnel JrVW has a manual zoom range from 15,5° to 83°, with precise focusing, and an 8-leaf barndoor (included).\nThis fixture has an intuitive user interface with rotatory knobs. It also has stand-alone settings, PowerCon True in & through connections and XLR in & through, offering an incredible user experience and easy setup.",
